					"body": "I'm using a HTC Desire Eye and when I used the first background fix, I get the results as [^fix_1.png]. The red outline is traced out on the whole app including beyond the navigation and status bar. Thus, needed the 1 pix black frame to get a better result as shown in [^fix_2.png]\r\n\r\nIf everything is okay, can I resolve this ticket?",
